28:36.324 --> 28:39.792
by the half-breed Klaus Mikaelson,

28:39.794 --> 28:42.495
and together, we are
going to liberate him.

28:42.497 --> 28:44.663
- ALL: Yeah!
- [APPLAUSE]

28:45.900 --> 28:48.434
We're gonna do more than that.

28:51.406 --> 28:53.172
