28:53.174 --> 28:57.243
We are going to end the Mikaelson rule,

28:57.245 --> 28:59.945
once and for all.

29:02.984 --> 29:04.583
[CHUCKLES]

29:04.585 --> 29:07.788
This city has known violence
a hell of a lot longer

29:07.791 --> 29:09.888
than it's known about our magic.

29:09.891 --> 29:12.591
I mean, that's why,
all those centuries ago,

29:12.593 --> 29:15.928
our ancestors created
the Ancestral Well.

29:15.930 --> 29:20.091
So that we would have
something, some sort of power,

29:20.094 --> 29:22.034
so that we could survive in this place.

29:22.036 --> 29:24.596
Like my mother, we must,
tonight, embrace a vision

29:24.599 --> 29:28.574
