has grown very, very toxic.

29:40.555 --> 29:45.057
Right now, our ancestors
are living in horror.

29:45.059 --> 29:48.894
Right now, our ancestors
don't have any peace.

29:48.896 --> 29:50.863
And that's why, tonight,

29:50.865 --> 29:53.666
we are going to release them.

29:53.668 --> 29:58.037
So that every single one
of our dead will be free.

29:58.039 --> 30:01.707
Tonight, we go to war.

30:01.709 --> 30:04.443
But those of you who are
not resolute in the belief

30:04.445 --> 30:09.715
that we are the one and
the only true species...

30:11.152 --> 30:15.568
...the time for you to leave is now.

30:15.571 --> 30:16.789
We're with you.

30:16.791 --> 30:18.290
ALL: Yes.

30:18.292 --> 30:19.658
VINCENT: <i>Once we release</i>

30:19.660 --> 30:21.160
the Ancestral Well,

30:21.162 --> 30:23.529
our ancestors are gonna know peace,

30:23.531 --> 30:27.466
but our power is gonna change forever.

30:27.468 --> 30:31.804
Our magic is gonna come
from the earth itself.

30:31.806 --> 30:33.806
But there ain't no turning back.

30:33.808 --> 30:36.108
So let's go ahead and do this.

30:36.110 --> 30:38.444
♪ Bothered with the teachers... ♪

30:38.446 --> 30:41.450
ALL [CHANTING]: <i>Libérez-nous.</i>

30:41.549 --> 30:43.182
<i>Libérez-nous.</i>

30:43.184 --> 30:45.317
<i>Libérez-nous. Libérez-nous.</i>

30:45.319 --> 30:47.682
ELIJAH: <i>Now, Greta died
in the name of purity,</i>

30:47.685 --> 30:50.322
and thanks to the unwavering
conviction of her followers,

30:50.324 --> 30:53.893
particularly those of you who
chose to lead when she was gone,

30:53.895 --> 30:56.795
her message lives on.

30:56.797 --> 31:00.099
So now, for those who stood by her,

31:00.101 --> 31:02.034
you will share her fate.

31:02.036 --> 31:03.969
- [PEOPLE MUTTERING]
- [DOORS OPEN]

31:03.971 --> 31:07.177
♪ It's not the same in here
since he left anyways... ♪

31:07.180 --> 31:09.182
What are they doing here?

31:09.185 --> 31:12.811
"The road to redemption is
long and winding, but worthy.”

31:14.315 --> 31:17.716
♪ Always said I was a good kid... ♪

31:19.421 --> 31:20.786
