31:25.026 --> 31:26.358
You can leave them to us now.

31:26.360 --> 31:28.894
♪ Ever break this curse ♪

31:28.896 --> 31:32.498
♪ Now the world is only white noise... ♪

31:32.500 --> 31:34.800
