31:36.404 --> 31:40.472
<i>- Ansanm non enim
- Libérez-nous...</i>

31:40.474 --> 31:45.185
<i>- liberari pour les morts.
- Libérez-nous... Libérez-nous...</i>

31:45.188 --> 31:49.524
VINCENT: <i>Ansanm non enim</i>

31:49.527 --> 31:52.027
- <i>liberari...</i>
- [WITCHES CONTINUE CHANTING]

31:52.030 --> 31:54.898
<i>pour les morts.</i>

31:54.901 --> 31:57.256
Go on, sweetheart,

31:57.258 --> 31:58.955
let it all out.

31:58.958 --> 32:03.028
♪ Momma told me all of this is ♪

32:03.030 --> 32:05.664
♪ Just a place we have to settle for... ♪

32:05.666 --> 32:09.535
- VINCENT: <i>Ansanm non enim...</i>
- WITCHES: <i>Libérez-nous...</i>

32:09.537 --> 32:11.503
<i>liberari...</i>

32:13.007 --> 32:16.575
♪ We'll continue to be disappointed... ♪

