35:47.354 --> 35:48.419
♪ Part of me ♪

35:48.421 --> 35:49.921
Yeah.

35:49.923 --> 35:52.393
It's so beautiful.

35:52.396 --> 35:54.359
♪ Will I recover ♪

35:54.361 --> 35:56.828
♪ That broken piece ♪

35:56.830 --> 36:00.365
♪ Let it go and unleash ♪

36:00.367 --> 36:01.866
Ivy...

