♪ All the feelings, ooh ♪

36:06.272 --> 36:08.706
Ivy?

36:08.708 --> 36:11.943
♪ Did we ever see it coming? ♪

36:11.945 --> 36:15.313
♪ Will we ever let it go? ♪

