♪ Without a plea ♪

36:30.916 --> 36:34.279
♪ I don't want to know ♪

36:34.282 --> 36:36.716
♪ What it's like ♪

36:36.719 --> 36:38.886
♪ To live without you ♪

36:38.889 --> 36:41.693
♪ Don't want to know the other side... ♪

36:41.696 --> 36:43.162
You know, it's funny you brought up

36:43.165 --> 36:45.928
