♪ Don't want to know ♪

37:49.008 --> 37:50.274
Aiden.

37:50.276 --> 37:52.043
♪ The other side ♪

37:52.045 --> 37:55.913
♪ Of a world without you... ♪

37:55.915 --> 37:57.982
Get in.

